name: What Happenned Before?
description:
In What Happenned Before you have to guess what historical events took place before (and later) than others. Do you consider yourself a true history buff? Break your own records until you can put in order every event in one single run.

Alternatively, you can play Videogames and Music modes where you will put chronologically in order... Videogames, songs and albums. Makes sense, right?
